            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="https://via.placeholder.com/350x150" alt="Noticias" />
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Noticia 2</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Texto Referente há noticia 2...</p>
                <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted">Atualizado a 15 Minutos</small></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="https://via.placeholder.com/350x150" alt="Noticias" />
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Noticia 3</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Texto Referente há noticia 3...</p>
